{"tid":2052659,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美記者微信密碼改成「F*ckCCP89」　帳號不足一分鐘後被永久關閉","createTime":"2020-06-05T16:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T17:45:05.000Z","uid":20933,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d925eff190d7b54f1c5729f048663b5d8b2b77","tid":2052659,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/post-19_83Fwf_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpost-19_83Fwf_1200x0.png&h=e33dfdbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以報導中國問題聞名的美籍記者貝書穎 (Bethany Allen-Ebrahimian) 今早在社交網站 Twitter 發帖文，指她嘗試將個人微信帳戶的密碼改成「FuckCCP89」以挑戰中國「底線」，但更改不足一分鐘後，其微信帳號卻被直接永久移除，沒有上訴程序，亦沒有暫時停用的畫面。貝書穎為美國新媒體 Axios 的記者，她曾任 ICIJ 中國組記者和《Foreign Policy》記者，亦參與過新疆再教育營的調查報道。<br />\n<br />\n貝書穎當時身處美國更改帳號密碼，其微信帳號也是使用美國的電話號碼。她又在 twitter 補充，自己是使用中國版的微信。<br />\n<br />\n對於帳號被移除，貝書穎表示不滿，但又對此經歷表示「有趣」，「原來國家的無形之手，可伸到所有地方 &mdash; 不論是公開的、私密的，準備就每個細節作出懲罰」(everywhere around, in places hidden and open, known and unknown, there is the hand of the state, waiting to punish every small infraction)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/美記者微信密碼改成-f-ckccp89-帳號不足一分鐘後被關閉/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E7%BE%8E%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E6%94%B9%E6%88%90-f-ckccp89-%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E4%B8%80%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%2F&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGTmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=0a0e627a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E7%BE%8E%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E6%94%B9%E6%88%90-f-ckccp89-%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E4%B8%80%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%2F&h=211a86ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/美記者微信密碼改成-f-ckccp8